# Decision Log — append-only, one JSON object per line (JSONL format)
#
# Records key decisions made during autonomous loop runs:
#   - HITL answers (human decisions that unblocked the loop)
#   - Implementation lock overrides
#   - Rejected alternatives during planning
#
# Schema per entry:
#   {"ts":"ISO8601Z","type":"hitl|lock_override|planning_rejection",
#    "ref":"PRD-001","by":"human|agent",
#    "question":"...(for hitl)","answer":"...(for hitl)",
#    "blocking_reason":"...(for hitl)","notes":"..."}
#
# Rules:
#   - Append only. Never edit existing lines.
#   - Written by ai/SKILL_HITL.prompt.md after human decision is recorded.
#   - To append: echo '<json>' >> docs/ai/decisions.jsonl
